#
Suggested directory layout:

  ./cmake
  ./cmake/modules	common cmake modules
  ./doc			common documentation
  ./doc/autodoc		libsnap docs created by doxygen
  ./doc/autoinclude	additional pages merged into autodoc
  ./examples		Example code
  ./package		BUID: specfile, tarball and changes file
  ./snap		libsnap sourcecode
  ./snapper		snapper sourcecode
  ./tests		testsuite

#
To setup a new build tree:

  mkdir BUILD_DIR
  cd    BUILD_DIR
  cmake SOURCE_DIR

If you want the BUILD_DIR being located inside the sourcetree, use
'BUILD' as directory name. This name is ignored by git (via .gitignore).
